<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="try-v">try <strong><em>v</em></strong> ★</h1>
<p>英 /traɪ/    美 /traɪ/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>尝试；试图；努力</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>Try</strong> your strength / <strong>luck</strong>. 
试试你的力气/碰碰你的运气吧。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>Try as she might</strong> (= as hard as she could), Sue couldn’t get the door open.
苏想尽办法，但是仍开不开门。</p><footer>2011 全国</footer></div>

<ul>
<li>try to do sth:</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Try not to become a man of success but rather try to become a man of value.
不要为成功而努力，而要为做一个有价值的人而努力。</p><footer>—— 爱因斯坦</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Bob <strong>tried hard to</strong> learn cooking, but the meals he prepared were terrible.
鲍勃非常努力地学习烹饪，但他做的饭菜很难吃。</p></div>

<ul>
<li>try one’s best (to do sth):</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She never gave up but tried her best to overcome the difficulty in life.
她从未放弃过，而是努力克服生活中的困难。</p></div>

<h3 id="manage-try">辨析 manage, try</h3>
<p><strong>manage</strong>  强调结果，表示经过一番努力之后做成某事。
**try ** 强调动作，不表示结果如何。</p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I’ll try to get downtown this afternoon but I don’t know if I can make it. 
今天下午我想去市中心，但不知是否能去成。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>试做；试用；试验：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>If I’m going out for a meal, I prefer to <strong>try something different</strong>. 
如果到外面吃饭，我喜欢尝试不同的饭菜。</p></div>

<ul>
<li>try doing sth:</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>John isn’t here. Try phoning his home number.
约翰不在这里，试试打他家里的电话。</p></div>

<p>注: 1. try doing sth 一般表示“尝试做某事”，含 有试试看的意味；try to do sth 则表示“努力做某 事”。2. 口语中，尤其在祈使句中，常用try and 代替 try to。  </p>
<h4 id="3">3.<strong>考验；磨炼：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>try sb’s courage 
考验某人的胆量</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="try-on">try on</h3>
<p>1.<strong>试穿：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I went to the tailor’s to try on my new suit.
我去裁缝店试穿我的新衣服。</p></div>

<h3 id="try-out">try out</h3>
<p>1.<strong>试验：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>try out an idea 
试验一种设想</p></div>

<h3 id="try-out-for">try out for</h3>
<p>1.<strong>参加…选拔 / 试演：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>All the students in the class tried out for the basketball match. 
班上的全体学生都参加了篮球选拔赛。</p></div>

<h2 id="_3">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>Susan wanted to be independent of her parents. She tried <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ (live) alone, but she didn’t like it and moved back home.   （2008 湖南改）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. living  </p></div>